<!--FAQ-->
<section class="about-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
        <h1 class="section-heading">FAQ</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="panel-group paddingDiv" id="accordion">

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1">
                I want to join alone, can I sign up alone?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">You may sign up alone, however the requirement is to form a team of 3 to 4.
              If you do not have a team, no worries, you may look for a team after signing up!</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2">
                Who are eligible to sign up?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">Any student from a local Institute of Higher Learning.
              That means whether you are from a polytechnic or university, you can join!</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3">
                Must I be in Singapore throughout the competition period?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">You need not be in Singapore! You may work remotely with your team. </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse4">
                Must I be present for the 2 days of Finale?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">You are encouraged to be present (so that you can collect your prizes yourself)!
              However, a team needs only at least one representative at the Finale.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse5">
                Must I be present for the closed-door pitching and the on-stage pitching?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">You are encouraged to be, but a team may send just one representative for both
              pitchings.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse6">
                What is the proposal submission method?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse6" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">Proposal will be submitted online, through the team portal. </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse7">
                When may I submit my proposal?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse7" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">You may submit the proposal, and amend it anytime from 5 April to 17 May. </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse8">
                Can I attempt more than one challenge?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse8" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">Each team is allowed to attempt only one track, and only one challenge statement from that track. </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse9">
                Can I join more than one team?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse9" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">Each participant is only allowed to join one team.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse10">
                Can I quit my team?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse10" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">You may quit your team. However a team with less than 3 members will be
              disqualified from entering the Finals. If the team is already in the Finals, it will be disqualified from winning.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse11">
                What happens if there is a conflict in my team?</a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse11" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">Teams are required to resolve any conflicts among themselves.
              The Organisers will not be responsible for the resolution of any conflicts, nor will the
              Organisers step in to mediate between the conflicting individuals or parties.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


