      <span>Collaboration</span>
      <br>where we collaborate with industry leaders, government agencies, student bodies to bring business IT to greater heights.<br><br>
      <span>Competition</span>
      <br>BiZiT organises challenges and competitions to bring out the best and the cream of the crop, and give them a chance to showcase their talents.<br><br>
